Changes:
 ros-jazzy-legged-control-base (3.3.0-2026.04.24.11.02) noble; urgency=high
 .
   * Add legged_bringup package with shared launch utilities
     Extract generate_temp_config, resolve_policy_paths, control_spawner,
     and download_wandb_onnx into a shared Python module to avoid duplication
     across robot bringup packages. Also makes --param-file mandatory on
     spawner per Jazzy migration.
     Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <mailto:noreply@anthropic.com>
   * Contributors: qiayuanl
